changeSet.author: ibewes
changeSet.comment: Update any incorrectly defined expiration dates that include a time portion. This will take into account the timezone for the server.
Update any detail records that are now duplicated (that is have the same stockroom, item, expiration, and batch).
changeSet.sql: UPDATE inv_item_stock_detail Z INNER JOIN (SELECT A.item_stock_detail_id, SUM(B.quantity) AS sum_quantity FROM inv_item_stock_detail A INNER JOIN inv_item_stock_detail B ON A.item_stock_detail_id < B.item_stock_detail_id AND A.item_id = B.item_id AND A.stockroom_id = B.stockroom_id AND A.expiration = B.expiration AND A.batch_operation_id = B.batch_operation_id WHERE A.item_stock_detail_id = (SELECT MIN(item_stock_detail_id) FROM inv_item_stock_detail WHERE item_id = A.item_id AND stockroom_id = A.stockroom_id AND expiration = A.expiration AND batch_operation_id = A.batch_operation_id) GROUP BY A.item_id, A.item_stock_detail_id, A.quantity) CALC ON Z.item_stock_detail_id = CALC.item_stock_detail_id SET Z.quantity = Z.quantity + CALC.sum_quantity;
changeSet.comment: Delete the duplicated records, leaving the only record that was updated.
changeSet.sql: DELETE A FROM inv_item_stock_detail AS A INNER JOIN inv_item_stock_detail AS B ON A.item_stock_detail_id > B.item_stock_detail_id AND A.item_id = B.item_id AND A.stockroom_id = B.stockroom_id AND A.expiration = B.expiration AND A.batch_operation_id = B.batch_operation_id;
changeSet.comment: Update operation items and transactions to add a single day if the timezone would have cause the date to be one day in the past
Finally, update the inv_item_stock_detail.expiration column to be only a DATE column, not DATETIME
Remove any invalid reservation transactions that are hanging around.
changeSet.sql: DELETE trans FROM inv_stock_operation op INNER JOIN inv_reserved_transaction trans ON op.stock_operation_id = trans.operation_id WHERE op.status = 'COMPLETED'

changeSet.createView: SELECT c.consumption_id, b.item_id, b.expiration, b.quantity - coalesce(SUM(c.quantity + c.wastage), 0) as quantity, a.department_id FROM inv_stock_operation a INNER JOIN inv_stock_operation_item b ON a.stock_operation_id=b.operation_id AND a.department_id is not null LEFT JOIN inv_consumption c ON b.item_batch = c.batch_number and a.department_id=c.department_id GROUP BY b.item_batch, b.expiration, a.department_id

changeSet.author: Toyeeb Abdulfatai
changeSet.createView: SELECT c.consumption_id, b.item_id, b.item_batch, a.commodity_type, DATE_FORMAT(a.date_created, '%Y-%m-%d') as date_created, b.expiration, b.quantity - coalesce(SUM(c.quantity + c.wastage), 0) as quantity, a.department_id FROM inv_stock_operation a INNER JOIN inv_stock_operation_item b ON a.stock_operation_id=b.operation_id AND a.department_id is not null LEFT JOIN inv_pharmacy_consumption c ON b.item_batch = c.batch_number and a.department_id=c.department_id where commodity_type='pharmacy' GROUP BY b.item_batch, b.expiration, a.department_id, a.commodity_type, a.date_created

changeSet.author: Toyeeb Abdulfatai
changeSet.createView: select tb1.stock_operation_id, tb2.item_batch, tb2.expiration, tb1.department_id, tb1.commodity_type, DATE_FORMAT(tb1.date_created, '%Y-%m-%d') as date_created, tb1.qtyReceived, tb2.qtyDistribute, (tb1.qtyReceived - qtyDistribute) as quantity, tb2.item_id from (select a.stock_operation_id, b.item_batch, b.expiration, a.department_id, a.commodity_type, a.date_created, sum(b.quantity) as qtyReceived, b.item_id from inv_stock_operation a inner join inv_stock_operation_item b ON a.stock_operation_id=b.operation_id where a.operation_type_id=4 and a.commodity_type='pharmacy' group by b.item_id order by b.item_id) as tb1 INNER JOIN (select a.stock_operation_id, b.item_batch, b.expiration, a.department_id, a.commodity_type, a.date_created, sum(b.quantity) as qtyDistribute, b.item_id from inv_stock_operation a inner join inv_stock_operation_item b ON a.stock_operation_id=b.operation_id where a.operation_type_id=3 and a.commodity_type='pharmacy' group by b.item_id order by b.item_id, a.department_id) as tb2 ON tb1.item_id=tb2.item_id
